on BusinessWire - BZX











Multimedia Platforms Inc.


            
            Multimedia Platforms, Inc.  is a multimedia, technology, and publishing company which delivers content and advertising. It integrates digital, mobile, streaming video, print and outdoor signage with social media and experiential events to deliver news, lifestyle and entertainment information of interest to customers and advertisers. The company was founded on April 3, 1996 and is headquartered in Fort Lauderdale, FL.

            
