All ShoeDazzle members who make a transaction utilizing their MasterCard on ShoeDazzle.com during the Promotion Period are eligible to receive a VIP Rewards Points Bonus. The VIP Rewards Points Bonus is valued at One Thousand (1,000) rewards points. Promotion Period is the first day of the month through the last day of the same month. Offer is only valid for ShoeDazzle VIP Members who utilize a MasterCard for their ShoeDazzle purchase. One Thousand (1,000) rewards points will be added to member's account on or before the Fifteenth (15th) of the following month after MasterCard transaction takes place. (Ex. Member who makes a purchase utilizing their MasterCard on ShoeDazzle.com on 07/02/2017, will have One Thousand (1,000) rewards points added to their account on or before 08/15/17 at 11:59 PM PST). Member is eligible to receive only one (1) One Thousand (1,000) VIP Rewards Points Bonus per month. Cannot be applied to any previous ShoeDazzle.com purchase that was processed utilizing a MasterCard. ShoeDazzle is not accountable for point balance discrepancies in the event point balances have already been spent or expired. Credit billings that are processed on a MasterCard during the Promotion Period are not eligible for the Rewards Points Bonus; member must actively make a product purchase utilizing their MasterCard. Credits can be applied toward Eligible MasterCard Purchase. Eligible MasterCard Purchase would need to be at least $.01 and completed during the Promotion Period. Points expire one (1) year from when points were added to member's account. Non-transferrable. ShoeDazzle is not responsible for any fraudulent activity or use of card. Cannot be redeemed for cash. ShoeDazzle's standard terms of service regarding shipping, returns, and exchanges apply. Terms subject to change at any time without notice. Must use a MasterCard for eligible transaction. 
	














